name: Vol 1., Ch.8:The End
description: Early in the morning Tiara woke up, still disoriented. She and all the girls were sleeping on the floor naked, covered by a dozen blankets. Her first thought was how beautiful her friends looked. Suddenly memories of last night started to pour back, and anxiety to creep in. A gently touch caressed  her arm, and she felt in peace again. “Don’t worry, we are are good friends here” Clair whispered. Tiara smiled.
